This example is from:
http://www.quantum-espresso.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/exercise2_instructions.pdf

Required input files are:

Al.sample.in
Al.pz-vbc.UPF

Downloaded from http://www.democritos.it/the-group/fig/Piccinin/Shared_files/exe_shanghai2013.tgz

Basic commands are:

module load espresso/5.0.3
pw.x < Al.sample.in > Al.sample.out
